creator: winkypinky
descriptionHtml:
Prepare yourself to encounter a wonderful kitty game where you actually get to know the routine of a fancy cat. There will be some steps you need to go through, but first, you must understand your cat needs. Four items from the bottom side of the screen will be your guide along this game; you will find that each one of them represents an important need of your kitty. The smiley face is for the good state of mind she might be into if you play interactive activities or if you have some sports exercise done. The food comes next and here you have to make sure she isn't hungry, then you will have the shower and the napping icon. All of them will be fulfilled once you go through each stop. In order to buy clothes, you will need money and you will gain some with your super farm. Cultivate fruits and vegetables to sell them. At the gym, you will have to keep Kitty Kate in a good shape, so you will help her out with the exercises. Don't forget to check her condition and if is necessary to be improved just look at the icon that indicates what she needs. After sport, she might need a refreshing nap and maybe something to eat, or even a shower. Next comes the dentist, which is a must and you have to take care of her teeth to be bright and healthy. Match an amazing hairstyle with her brand new cleaned teeth from the salon section. Use your imagination and add accessories too. Also, you can increase her unique style with some fresh bought clothes. Go to the mall to find the perfect look that will help Kitty Kate to unleash her beauty.

There are plenty of cool features this awesome animal game provides you just have to look after them, and if not, you could spot them right below:
- Opportunity to take care of a little cat
- Design wonderful outfits and try a lovely hairstyle from the wardrobe
- Crazy accessories and interesting gym moves
- Be a caretaker as much as a hairstylist for kitties
- Free and pretty easy to play
- Making educational activities
- Multiple levels to go through
- Illustrating graphics and interesting gameplay
descriptionShort: Find out how this kitty is getting her glamour in this caring game.
